To stop voluntary attrition, we suggest increasing emotional connection employees have to their companies. We would do that by: 
 1) giving special titles to those who have worked for a certain period of time;
 2) giving each employee a pet - a cat/dog/turtle/fish/rat/spider/etc. - when they join the company. If employees leave, they loose the pet because the said animal lives in the office.
